These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
City: colone, prague, nizza, venice, berlin, rome, paris
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, baccarat, alhambra, pall-mall, chaman, ritmeester, aristoff
 1. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to berlin is the dutch##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is the person traveling to nizza##1
 4. the british is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person traveling to nizza##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the swisher-smoker##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the alhambra-smoker##1
15. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the german##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| City         | nizza | berlin | colone | prague | paris  | rome  | venice    |
| Cigar     | chaman  | ritmeester         | swisher     | baccarat    | alhambra | pall-mall     | aristoff     |

